CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 26 reads: " Thousands Thrilled at Courier Home Service Fair...2. Mrs. Louise R. Protho Pet Milk Company home economist and national demonstrator fro the fourteen nation-wide Courier Home Shows, demonstrates her culinary artistry as she held an attentive audience of thousands spellbound. She was assisted by Pittsburgh's Mrs. Mary Ellen Nelson...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: PET home economist Louise R. Protho conducting cooking demonstration with Mary Ellen Nelson on stage with Norge Appliances in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
